In the distance, a large white bridge with a curved arch design stretches across the scene. The bridge's white color stands out against the blue sky, which is lightly speckled with a few clouds. 

On the right side of the street, there's a building with a facade painted in shades of gray and white. A car is parked on the street, adding a touch of everyday life to the scene. On the left side of the street, a street lamp stands tall, ready to illuminate the area as dusk falls. 

The image is a blend of urban architecture and natural elements, showcasing the harmonious coexistence of man-made structures and nature in Beijing.
